import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container';
import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav';
import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';
import './header.css';

export default function AppHeader() {
    return (
        <>
            <Navbar className="bg-body-tertiary" expand="lg">
                <Container>
                    <Navbar.Brand href="#home">WANDERLOGIXS</Navbar.Brand>
                    <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
                    <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
                        <Nav className="me-auto custom-nav-spacing">
                            <Nav.Link href="#dashboard">Dashboard</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="#trips">Trips</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="#link">Expenses</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="#link">Itinerary</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="#link">Media</Nav.Link>
                            <Nav.Link href="#link" style={{ marginRight: '20px' }}>Itinerary</Nav.Link>
                        </Nav>
                        <Form className="d-flex">
                            <Form.Control
                                type="search"
                                placeholder="Search"
                                className="me-2"
                                aria-label="Search"
                            />
                                <Button type="submit">Submit</Button>

                        </Form>
                    </Navbar.Collapse>
                </Container>
            </Navbar>
        </>
    );
}
